《'''根'''》（{{lang-en|Roots}}）是一部美国[[迷你剧集|迷你剧集]]，改编自[[艾利斯·哈利|艾利斯·哈利]]于1976年创作的小说《[[根：一个美国家庭的传奇|根：一个美国家庭的传奇]]》。该剧集于1977年1月在[[美国广播公司|美国广播公司]]频道中首播。《根》获得了37项[[黃金時段艾美獎|黄金时段艾美奖]]提名，并斩获9个项大奖。它还获得了[[金球獎|金球奖]]和[[皮博迪獎|皮博迪奖]]。该剧的大结局获得了史无前例的[[尼爾森收視率|尼尔森收视成绩]]，至今仍然是所有电视连续剧中[[尼爾森收視率|收视率]]第三高的一集，也是美国电视史上收视率第二高的电视连续剧大结局。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Top 100 Rated TV Shows of All Time, TV By the Numbers|url=http://tvbythenumbers.com/2009/03/21/top-100-rated-tv-shows-of-all-time/14922|accessdate=November 17, 2012|publisher=Tvbythenumbers.com|archive-date=2012-10-02|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6B6XUXF0o?url=http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2009/03/21/top-100-rated-tv-shows-of-all-time/14922/|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{Cite book|last=Hyatt|first=Wesley|title=Television's Top 100|year=2012|publisher=McFarland|location=US|isbn=978-0-7864-4891-3|page=167|url=https://mcfarlandbooks.com/product/televisions-top-100/|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110326163815/http://www.mcfarlandpub.com/book-2.php?id=978-0-7864-4891-3|archivedate=March 26, 2011|accessdate=December 19, 2018}}</ref>剧集的制作预算为660万美元。<ref name="budget2">{{Cite news|title=New Roots series expected to yield big bucks for ABC|page=54|work=[[Ottawa_Citizen|Ottawa Citizen]]|date=February 20, 1979|accessdate=February 28, 2010|url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=t0MzAAAAIBAJ&dq=cost%20abc%20%246%20million%20and%20ran%2012%20hours&pg=5309%2C265933|archive-date=2021-01-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210108201240/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=t0MzAAAAIBAJ&dq=cost%20abc%20$6%20million%20and%20ran%2012%20hours&pg=5309,265933|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="budget1">{{Cite news|title=Roots...Second Time Around|page=2|first=Brian|author=Courtis|work=[[The_Age|The Age]]|date=February 19, 1979|accessdate=February 25, 2010|url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=QdoQAAAAIBAJ&dq=roots%20the%20next%20generations%20ratings&pg=4550%2C1703582}}</ref>

[[续集|续集]]《[[根：下一代|根：下一代]]》于1979年首播，第二部续集，由由伯顿和小[[小路易斯·格塞特|路易斯·歌塞特]]主演的圣诞电影《根：礼物》于1988年上映。

2016年，[[歷史頻道|历史频道]]投资重拍了同名迷你剧，并在[[亡兵紀念日|阵亡将士纪念日]]放映。

== 反响 ==
该剧集获得诸多好评。评论聚合网站[[爛番茄|烂番茄]]根据8个评论意见，将该剧评为88％“新鲜”度。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Roots: Miniseries|url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/tv/roots_1977/s01|accessdate=17 June 2020|archive-date=2018-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180126192413/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/tv/roots_1977/s01/|dead-url=no}}</ref>《[[綜藝_(雜誌)|综艺]]》杂志给予该剧证明评价，总结道：“制作和表演都十分扎实，新人勒瓦尔·伯顿饰演一名来自非洲、被困为奴的年轻人的演出令人信服。爱德华·阿斯纳的表现就像一年前他在《悲欢岁月》中所做的一样，从一出场就统治了荧幕。”<ref>{{Cite web|title=Roots|url=https://variety.com/1977/tv/reviews/roots-1200423818/|date=22 January 1977|access-date=2021-02-07|archive-date=2020-11-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201123173732/https://variety.com/1977/tv/reviews/roots-1200423818/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 播出历史 ==
=== 分集列表 ===
1977年1月23日至30日，《根》在[[美国广播公司|美国广播公司]]频道上连续八晚播出。在[[英国|英国]]，[[英國廣播公司第一台|英國廣播公司第一台]]将该剧拆分为六部分播出，1977年4月8日至11日这个周末播出第一部分到第三部分。4月15日至5月1日的周日晚上播出后三部分。英国广播公司播出的分六部的版本是最后通过家庭录影发布的版本。

=== 美国电视收视率 ===
该迷你电视剧的收视观众总数预计约为1.3亿<ref name="time">{{Cite journal|title=Television: A Super Sequel to Haley's Comet|url=http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,912386,00.html|last=Rich|first=Frank|date=February 18, 1979|journal=Time|accessdate=February 26, 2010|archive-date=2012-10-02|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6B6XTErZA?url=http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,912386,00.html|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name="schen">{{Cite news|title=ABC Soard in Ratings With 'Roots' Sequel|page=12|work=[[The_Daily_Gazette|Schenectady Gazette]]|date=February 24, 1979|accessdate=February 26, 2010|url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=MgwhAAAAIBAJ&dq=roots%20the%20next%20generations%20ratings&pg=1194%2C7147519|archive-date=2021-11-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211104124435/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=MgwhAAAAIBAJ&dq=roots%20the%20next%20generations%20ratings&pg=1194,7147519|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="tuscaloosa">{{Cite news|title=110 million see 'Roots' video special|page=8|work=[[The_Tuscaloosa_News|The Tuscaloosa News]]|date=March 1, 1979|accessdate=February 26, 2010|url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=nDAdAAAAIBAJ&dq=roots%20the%20next%20generations%20ratings&pg=6626%2C36002|archive-date=2021-07-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210703082524/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=nDAdAAAAIBAJ&dq=roots%20the%20next%20generations%20ratings&pg=6626%2C36002|dead-url=no}}</ref>至1.4亿<ref name="pitt">{{Cite news|title='Roots' Ratings Dip|page=29|work=[[Pittsburgh_Post-Gazette|Pittsburgh Post-Gazette]]|date=February 28, 1979|accessdate=February 26, 2010|url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=MkwNAAAAIBAJ&dq=roots%20the%20next%20generations%20ratings&pg=4905%2C3529170}}</ref><ref name="bryan">{{Cite news|title=ABC Takes "Roots" Again|first=Joan|author=Hanauer|work=[[The_Bryan_Times|The Bryan Times]]|date=February 28, 1979|accessdate=February 26, 2010|url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=-xMpAAAAIBAJ&dq=roots%20the%20next%20generations%20ratings&pg=5350%2C4725707|archive-date=2021-10-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211026075108/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=-xMpAAAAIBAJ&dq=roots%20the%20next%20generations%20ratings&pg=5350%2C4725707|dead-url=no}}</ref>（超过美国1977年人口总数2.21亿的半数，是尼尔森统计史上最高的数字），平均收视率为44.9  ，收视占比则为66%至80%。最后一集的收视人数为1亿，最后七集集均收视人数为8千万人。<ref name="museum">{{Cite web|title=Museum of Broadcast Communications|url=http://www.museum.tv/archives/etv/R/htmlR/roots/roots.htm|accessdate=November 17, 2012|publisher=Museum.tv|archive-date=2013-04-10|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6FlLQuXOE?url=http://www.museum.tv/eotvsection.php?entrycode=roots|dead-url=yes}}</ref>所有电视家庭中有85%的家庭看过全剧或部分集数。各集均排在有史以来收视率最高的100个电视节目之列。<ref name="top100">{{Cite web|title=Top 100 Rated TV Shows of All Time|url=http://tvbythenumbers.com/2009/03/21/top-100-rated-tv-shows-of-all-time/14922|accessdate=February 17, 2010|author=Gorman|date=May 21, 2009|first=Bill|archive-date=2012-10-02|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6B6XUXF0o?url=http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2009/03/21/top-100-rated-tv-shows-of-all-time/14922/|dead-url=yes}}</ref> <ref>{{Cite web|title=Nielsen Ratings: Top Programs of 1990-91|url=https://library.uoregon.edu/sites/default/files/data/guides/english/television_almanac.pdf|accessdate=June 21, 2015|work=University of Oregon|archive-date=2016-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305024447/https://library.uoregon.edu/sites/default/files/data/guides/english/television_almanac.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>
